        Introduction
        ============
        
        
        Requirements
        ============
        
        * RabbitMQ
        * RabbitMQ Management plugin
        * rabbitmqadmin cli
        
        
        Tests
        =====
        
        This package is tested using Travis CI. The current status of the add-on is :
        
